 with decomposition, which describes how two-dimensional\ntheories with one-form symmetries (such as pure gauge theories with nontrivial\ncenters) decompose into disjoint unions, in this case of pure gauge theories\nwith quotiented gauge groups and discrete theta angles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 18:04:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 20:25:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-03"}
