 applications. Extensive experiments show that the proposed methods can\nachieve much faster convergence and competitive performance even with very\nsmall size of training data, when compared with state-of-art algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 18:49:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 May 2020 10:14:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-02"}
